{"title":"GIVEAWAY: Answer a short survey for a chance to win carbon handlebars, cranks, and wheels from Race Face","link":"https://bikerumor.com/giveaway-answer-a-short-survey-for-a-chance-to-win-carbon-handlebars-cranks-and-wheels-from-race-face/","date":1695745263000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2158\" height=\"1432\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero.jpg\" alt loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero.jpg 2158w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero-297x197.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero-800x531.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero-768x510.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero-1536x1019.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-hero-2048x1359.jpg 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Itâ€™s never been easier to score a sweet upgrade from Race Face!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the next two weeks, readers can answer a quick survey for the chance to win <a href=\"https://www.raceface.com/collections/carbon-confidence\" target=\"_blank\">carbon Race Face equipment</a> courtesy of Fox Factory.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Each winner will receive a full package including an Era Crank, Next R 35 Handlebars, and Next R Wheels, all of which retail for a combined total of around $1,500.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NEXT Era Crank</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-800x532.jpg\" alt=\"Race Face Era crank mounted to a mountain bike. Side view.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-800x532.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-297x197.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-768x511.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-1536x1021.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-2048x1362.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-face-ERA-FINAL-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Race Face says its Era crank is the lightest and stiffest crank the brand has ever made. (Photo/Race Face)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Race Face says <a href=\"https://www.raceface.com/products/era-crankset?variant=40209683382354\" target=\"_blank\">the Era crank</a> is the strongest, stiffest, and most durable crank the brand has ever produced. It includes a stainless steel plate that guards against wear and tear from rubbing shoes and is backed up by a lifetime warranty.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Next R 35 Handlebar</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-scaled.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"552\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-800x552.jpeg\" alt=\"Race Face Next R handlebar. Front view.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-800x552.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-297x205.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-120x83.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-768x530.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-1536x1060.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-35-handlebar-2048x1413.jpeg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Race Faxe Next R Handlebar; (Photo/Race Face)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.raceface.com/products/next-r-35-handlebar?variant=31959208722514\">Next R 35 Handlebar</a> features unidirectional carbon treated with a matte clear coat. The result is a bar with the right amount of flex for reliable handling. The bars are 800mm wide out of the box, but include cut marks to bring them down to 750mm for those who prefer a narrower bar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Next R Wheels</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-scaled.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"552\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-800x552.jpeg\" alt=\"Race Face Next R wheel. Side view.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-800x552.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-297x205.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-120x83.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-768x530.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-1536x1060.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Race-Face-Next-R-Wheel-2048x1413.jpeg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Race Face Next R wheel; (Photo/Race Face)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.raceface.com/products/next-r-31-wheelset?variant=32058698825810\">Next R wheels</a> feature the same unidirectional carbon layup as the Next R handlebars, making them ideal for XC or trail riding. The wheels come laced with double-butted straight-pull spokes built around a Vault hub.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Answer the questions below for your chance to win!</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/giveaway-answer-a-short-survey-for-a-chance-to-win-carbon-handlebars-cranks-and-wheels-from-race-face/\">GIVEAWAY: Answer a short survey for a chance to win carbon handlebars, cranks, and wheels from Race Face</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Mark Wilson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9f1fb2aa0f33435e595aee2e220578338ba961576ab344eac869fd58f9335279","category":"Cycling"}